info.name: YouTube – Dark 2015
info.description: This is a darker black version of YouTube which is easier on the eyes. Please keep in mind that this is a work in progress and I am working on it as much as I can, however if you find something that I have forgot - please let me know in the comments! Please leave a rating if you liked the userstyle!
info.additionalInfo: Sep 09, 2014 - initial release Sep 10, 2014 - minor updates Sep 11, 2014 - fixed settings pages Sep 12, 2014 - fixed account pages Sep 13, 2014 - minor fixes to the subscriber button Sep 14, 2014 - fixed a few things Sep 15, 2014 - fixed the color of the html player to match the userstyle (HTML player ONLY) Sep 16, 2014 - added darker scrollbars (Only supported for WebKit browsers at this time) Sep 17, 2014 - fixed an error with the scrollbars Sep 25, 2014 - fixed subscription preferences popup Sep 26, 2014 - few fixes Oct 01, 2014 - fixed the chat during streams among lots of other things Oct 08, 2014 - fixed the creator bar under your own videos and the video manager Oct 10, 2014 - updated links Oct 11, 2014 - few changes to the uploading page Oct 12, 2014 - fixed lot of things I have missed (thanks to Sleekness) Oct 13, 2014 - fixed the reply-input box Oct 15, 2014 - updated shared posts and fixed iv cards that some YouTube videos has (with HTML5 enabled) Oct 21, 2014 - fixed the "Up Next" on the autoplay-bar Nov 01, 2014 - fixed and updated the like, dislike (ect) buttons and the icons in the "add-to"-list Nov 07, 2014 - fixed the music charts lists Nov 14, 2014 - fixed lots of new things (thanks to Sleekness for pointing most of them out) Nov 15, 2014 - few things that was left out is now fixed, adjusted few errors as well Nov 19, 2014 - fixed the updated images and and other things Jan 09, 2015 - fixed the 'all comments'-page Jan 30, 2015 - fixed the thumb-ratings Feb 04, 2015 - YouTube updated the thumb-ratings again, should be fixed again Feb 12, 2015 - minor updates Feb 14, 2015 - few corrections Mar 31, 2015 - fixed Video Manager May 01, 2015 - fixed the player-api background

data.title: Just thinking up some small changes
